reviewText: I love this movie. I watched it as a child and have such fond memories of it. The songs are still stuck in my head. Great for any child!

A very cute video.  It's nice to see a king who is happy and jolly instead of being impetuous and prone to angry outbursts.  And the part near the end where a boy gives King Cole his most prized possession is quite touching.  Next stop:  "The Big Rock Candy Mountains"? --- Paul H!
